    "body": "FYI, managed to update my docker-compose.yml file to use the 3 node setup described in [your doc](https://geth.ethereum.org/docs/fundamentals/private-network )\r\n\r\nThis might be helpful to others, the docker-compose.yml allow you to specify your custom genesis\r\n\r\nit uses a bootnode a miner node and an rpc node\r\n\r\nSee: https://github.com/wighawag/ethereum-lan-node/blob/0c3f6e50a2fb9f899a71ecf0d504140efe24fa21/docker-compose.yml\r\n\r\nIt works but would love to have the same thing as --dev with only one node running",
